<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Unigenome <%= project_id %></title>

    <!-- Dependencies -->
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/3.9.1/chart.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #F97316;
            --primary-hover: #EA580C;
            --primary-light: #FFF7ED;
            --secondary-color: #0F172A;
            --secondary-light: #1E293B;
            --accent-color: #3B82F6;
            --text-main: #0F172A;
            --text-muted: #64748B;
            --text-light: #94A3B8;
            --bg-body: #F8FAFC;
            --bg-sidebar: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);
            --bg-paper: #FFFFFF;
            --border-color: #E2E8F0;
            --card-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
            --card-shadow-hover: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
            --glass-blur: blur(16px);
            --radius-md: 12px;
            --radius-lg: 20px;
            --radius-xl: 24px;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--text-main);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F8FAFC 0%, #F1F5F9 100%);
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 300px;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            print-color-adjust: exact;
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, h4, .ui-font {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', 'Georgia', serif;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin: 0;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            text-align: justify;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        a {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-hover);
        }

        .section {
            scroll-margin-top: 50px;
        }

        /* Fixed TOC Sidebar Style */
        #TOC {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 300px;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
            background: var(--bg-sidebar);
            backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
            border-right: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 36px 0 40px;
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            box-shadow: 2px 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
        }

        /* Custom Scrollbar */
        #TOC::-webkit-scrollbar, body::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 8px;
        }

        #TOC::-webkit-scrollbar-track, body::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: transparent;
        }

        #TOC::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb, body::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background 0.2s ease;
        }

        #TOC::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover, body::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: var(--text-light);
        }

        /* Mobile Sidebar Toggle */
        #mobile-toc-toggle {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 24px;
            right: 24px;
            width: 56px;
            height: 56px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--primary-hover) 100%);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3);
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            z-index: 1010;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 28px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        #mobile-toc-toggle:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.35);
        }

        .toc-header {
            padding: 0 28px 28px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .toc-header img {
            max-width: 160px;
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: block;
        }

        .toc-header .project-id {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.03em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        #TOC ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0 16px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        #TOC li a {
            display: block;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            margin: 2px 0;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        #TOC li a:hover {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            background: var(--primary-light);
        }

        #TOC li a.active {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            background: var(--primary-light);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        /* Sidebar Submenu */
        #TOC ul.toc-submenu {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
            margin: 4px 0 0;
            max-height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: all 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        #TOC ul.toc-submenu.expanded {
            max-height: 600px;
            opacity: 1;
        }

        #TOC li.has-children > .toc-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 2px 0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        #TOC li.has-children > .toc-row:hover {
            background: var(--primary-light);
        }

        #TOC li.has-children > .toc-row.active-row {
            background: var(--primary-light);
        }

        #TOC li.has-children > .toc-row a {
            flex-grow: 1;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 10px 12px 10px 16px;
            border-radius: 10px 0 0 10px;
        }

        #TOC li.has-children > .toc-row a.active {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .toc-toggle-btn {
            padding: 10px 16px 10px 8px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
        }

        .toc-toggle-btn:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .toc-toggle-btn i {
            transition: transform 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        .toc-toggle-btn.rotated i {
            transform: rotate(180deg);
        }

        /* Sidebar Subsection Indentation */
        #TOC li a.toc-level-2 {
            padding-left: 32px;
            font-size: 13.5px;
        }

        #TOC li a.toc-level-3 {
            padding-left: 48px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        /* Main Content Area */
        .main-container {
            margin: 48px auto;
            padding: 0 56px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            background: transparent;
        }

        /* Cover Page */
        .cover-page {
            min-height: 90vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 40px 80px;
            page-break-after: always;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin-bottom: 56px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .cover-logo {
            max-width: 220px;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05));
        }

        .cover-title {
            font-size: 40px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .cover-subtitle {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            margin-bottom: 32px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        }

        .cover-details {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .submitted-by {
            margin-top: 32px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .submitted-to {
            margin-top: auto;
            padding-top: 32px;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .submitted-to .client-name {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 8px 0 4px;
            display: block;
        }

        .submitted-to .client-org {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .confidential-footer {
            width: 100%;
            border-top: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
            padding-top: 16px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* Typography */
        h1.title {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 36px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .section {
            scroll-margin-top: 60px;
            background-color: var(--bg-paper);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            padding: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            page-break-inside: avoid;
            transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .section:hover {
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow-hover);
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 26px;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            border-bottom: none;
            padding-bottom: 0;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            page-break-after: avoid;
        }

        h2::before {
            content: '';
            width: 6px;
            height: 32px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--primary-hover) 100%);
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            page-break-after: avoid;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        h4 {
            font-size: 17px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        /* Tables */
        .table-wrapper {
            overflow-x: auto;
            margin: 24px 0 32px;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }

        .table-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 100%;
            border-spacing: 0;
            border-collapse: separate;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        table th {
            padding: 14px 16px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--secondary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-light) 100%);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        table td {
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            vertical-align: middle;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
        }

        table tr:nth-of-type(even) td {
            background-color: #F8FAFC;
        }

        table tr:hover td {
            background-color: #F1F5F9;
        }

        /* Figures */
        .figure {
            margin: 36px 0;
            text-align: center;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }

        .figure img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .caption {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 16px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Info Box */
        .info-box {
            padding: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-color);
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-light) 0%, #FFFFFF 100%);
            color: var(--text-main);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
        }

        /* Tapestation Grid */
        .tapestation-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }

        .tapestation-card {
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background: #FFFFFF;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            page-break-inside: avoid;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .tapestation-card:hover {
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow-hover);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .tapestation-card img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            max-height: 400px;
            object-fit: contain;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding-bottom: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .tapestation-card span {
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            display: block;
        }

        /* Inline TOC */
        .inline-toc {
            page-break-after: always;
            padding: 48px;
            background: var(--bg-paper);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
        }

        .toc-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0 auto;
            max-width: 700px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            line-height: 2;
        }

        .toc-list li {
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .toc-list li.level-1 {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }

        .toc-list li.level-2 {
            padding-left: 28px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .toc-list li.level-3 {
            padding-left: 56px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .toc-list a {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-end;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-main);
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .toc-list a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        .toc-list .title {
            white-space: normal;
        }

        .toc-list .dots {
            flex-grow: 1;
            border-bottom: 2px dotted var(--border-color);
            margin: 0 10px;
            position: relative;
            top: -4px;
        }

        .toc-list .page {
            white-space: nowrap;
            text-align: right;
            min-width: 30px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .toc-list li.level-2 .page,
        .toc-list li.level-3 .page {
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .mono {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        /* Responsive Styles */
        @media screen and (max-width: 1200px) {
            body {
                padding-left: 0;
            }

            #TOC {
                transform: translateX(-100%);
            }

            #TOC.open {
                transform: translateX(0);
            }

            #mobile-toc-toggle {
                display: flex;
            }

            .main-container {
                margin: 24px;
                padding: 0;
            }

            .section, .inline-toc {
                padding: 32px;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
            .main-container {
                margin: 16px;
            }

            .cover-page {
                padding: 40px 24px 60px;
            }

            .cover-title {
                font-size: 30px;
            }

            .cover-subtitle {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .section, .inline-toc {
                padding: 24px;
            }

            h1.title {
                font-size: 26px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 22px;
            }

            h3 {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
        }

        /* Print Formatting */
        @media print {
            @page {
                size: A4;
                margin: 20mm 20mm 20mm 20mm;
            }

            @page :first {
                margin: 0;
            }

            body {
                background-color: #fff !important;
                font-size: 11pt;
                line-height: 1.6;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0 !important;
                width: 100% !important;
            }

            #TOC, #mobile-toc-toggle {
                display: none;
            }

            .main-container {
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 0;
                width: 100%;
                max-width: none;
                background: transparent;
                box-shadow: none;
                border-radius: 0;
                border: none;
            }

            .table-wrapper, table, .figure, .section, .inline-toc {
                break-inside: avoid;
            }

            .section, .inline-toc {
                box-shadow: none;
                border: none;
                padding: 0 0 32px;
            }

            .cover-page {
                box-shadow: none;
                border: none;
                border-radius: 0;
            }

            thead {
                display: table-header-group;
            }

            h2 {
                page-break-after: avoid;
                page-break-before: auto;
                margin-top: 30px;
            }

            h3 {
                page-break-after: avoid;
                page-break-before: auto;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div id="TOC">
        <div class="toc-header">
            <img src="<%= logo_path %>" alt="Unigenome Logo">
            <div class="project-id">NGS ID: <%= project_id %></div>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="#section-1" class="active">1 Project Details</a></li>
            <li><a href="#section-2">2 Sample Details</a></li>

            <li class="has-children">
                <div class="toc-row">
                    <a href="#section-3">3 Methods</a>
                    <span class="toc-toggle-btn"><i data-lucide="chevron-down" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"></i></span>
                </div>
                <ul class="toc-submenu">
                    <li><a href="#section-3" class="toc-level-2">3.1. Isolation and Quantitative analysis of RNA:</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#section-3" class="toc-level-2">3.2. Preparation of Library</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#section-3" class="toc-level-2">3.3. Quantity and quality check (QC) of library on Agilent Tape Station 4150</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#section-3" class="toc-level-2">3.4. Cluster Generation and Sequencing</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#section-3" class="toc-level-2">3.5. Results: RNA QC on 1.0% agarose gel</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#section-3" class="toc-level-2">3.6. Quantification using Qubit 4.0 Fluorometer</a></li>
                </ul>
            </li>

            <li class="has-children">
                <div class="toc-row">
                    <a href="#section-4">4 Library QC</a>
                    <span class="toc-toggle-btn"><i data-lucide="chevron-down" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"></i></span>
                </div>
                <ul class="toc-submenu">
                    <li><a href="#section-4" class="toc-level-2">4.1. TapeStation 4150 profiles of library loaded in Agilent High Sensitivity D1000ScreenTape&reg;:</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#section-4" class="toc-level-2">4.2. Wet Lab Inferences</a></li>
                </ul>
            </li>

            <li class="has-children">
                <div class="toc-row">
                    <a href="#section-5">5 Bioinformatics Analysis</a>
                    <span class="toc-toggle-btn"><i data-lucide="chevron-down" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"></i></span>
                </div>
                <ul class="toc-submenu">
                    <li><a href="#section-5" class="toc-level-2">5.1. Bioinformatics Workflow</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#section-5" class="toc-level-2">5.2. Detail of Software used for analysis</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#section-6" class="toc-level-2">5.3. Data statistics</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#section-7" class="toc-level-2">5.4. Reference genome information</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#section-8" class="toc-level-2">5.5. Mapping to reference genome</a></li>

                    <li class="has-children">
                        <div class="toc-row">
                            <a href="#section-9" class="toc-level-2">5.6. Transcript assembly</a>
                            <span class="toc-toggle-btn"><i data-lucide="chevron-down" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"></i></span>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="toc-submenu">
                            <li><a href="#section-9" class="toc-level-3">5.7. Comparison of assembled transcripts with reference transcripts</a></li>
                            <li><a href="#section-9" class="toc-level-3">5.7.1. Identification of novel isoform transcripts</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>

                    <li class="has-children">
                        <div class="toc-row">
                            <a href="#section-10" class="toc-level-2">5.8. Differential expression analysis</a>
                            <span class="toc-toggle-btn"><i data-lucide="chevron-down" style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"></i></span>
                        </div>
                        <ul class="toc-submenu">
